void '''SetHudWrapWidth''' (int ''wrapwidth'');

==Usage==
Sets the wrapping width for future HUD messages without altering the clipping rectangle. If you set the wrapping width to 0, messages will wrap
to the full width of the HUD, as normal.

===Parameters===
* ''wrapwidth'' 
